room_title: Escape room "Immunity Quest" by Locked in Fun in Chicago
room_description: Your tribe has been placed on a deserted island and must work as a team to solve puzzles and riddles in search of your immunity mask. But beware, not all things are as they seem on the island. To escape the island, you will need to find your immunity mask in time to make the only boat leaving the island in 45 minutes. Without your mask, you will surely be left behind.
